text: "I'm here on official business. Leave immediately."
"I have no obligation to answer any of your questions."
"Imma fuck you up if you don't give me some answers."
"Hey calm down, I just want to talk."
"Nope. Nice try, but I'm not telling you anything."
"I guess I'm wasting my time here."
"I'm not leaving until you tell me who you are."
"You don't even know what I'm doing here."
"What are you doing here? Do you work here or something?"
"To be honest I don't know what I'm doing here, I haven't been paying attention."
"You're being fucking weird. Leave before I make you."

"You work here too, hm? You might be useful to me...eventually...but you seem a little inexperienced. How about we make a deal? You turn a blind eye to me for now, maybe I'll get in touch with you later."
"No deal. You're up to something weird and I don't like it." (╬ Ò﹏Ó)
"I doubt you'll be able to help me. Leave now."
"Then be a good little agent and leave me be for now."
"We have nothing to talk about. There was a chiplet in the last room. Take it as your reward for finding me here, and begone."
